crm114 comes with its own set of mailing lists. These are used for 
discussions about crm114 development and usage. You can post your 
questions, suggestions or bug reports there.

Official language for these lists is english.

This mailing lists are hosted at the sourceforge site for free.

CRM114 also comes with a WIKI site ( http://crm114.sourceforge.net/wiki/ )
where a lot of information can be found.

To subscribe to a CRM114 mailing list, visit the wiki at

    http://crm114.sourceforge.net/wiki/

and click on the 'Mailing Lists' link in the left panel for more info.
